OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be
OL,6,Fmostly dry with bright or clear spells
OL,7,Fin the north and the east. Cloudy with
OL,8,Frain at times in the west and the
OL,9,Fsouth.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSunday:FCloudy with patchy rain in the
OL,12,Fsouth and west at first otherwise
OL,13,Fmostly dry with bright spells and the
OL,14,Fodd inland afternoon shower but dry
OL,15,Ffor most.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMostly
OL,18,Fdry and bright Monday then cloudy with
OL,19,Fpatchy rain and showers Tuesday. Dry
OL,20,Fat first Wednesday then cloud and rain
OL,21,Fspread east later.
